OL,6,FBut at the same time, we are faced
OL,7,Fwith the horrifying truth that there
OL,8,Fwere more than 8,200 alcohol deaths in
OL,9,FEngland in 2023 according to the
OL,10,Fgovernment - a record high and
OL,11,Fmeteoric 42% increase since 2019.
OL,13,FThis has led to stark warnings from
OL,14,Fcharities such as the Alcohol Health
OL,15,FAlliance, who this Christmas said the
OL,16,F"alcoholharm crisis" will only
OL,17,Fescalate if action is not taken to
OL,18,Freduce consumption.
