OL,6,FThe government responded saying their
OL,7,Ften year plan will shift focus from
OL,8,Fsickness to prevention ` prioritising
OL,9,Fmeasures to support people living
OL,10,Flonger.
OL,12,FBut the picture across the UK as a
OL,13,Fwhole is also bleak, with the Office
OL,14,Ffor National Statistics stating there
OL,15,Fwere 10,048 deaths from alcohol-
OL,16,Fspecific causes registered in 2022 -
OL,17,Fanother record figure.
