OL,6,FI was 14 when I discovered vodka. It
OL,7,Fwas the alcohol of choice for me and
OL,8,Fmy friends because we could drink it
OL,9,Fquickly before it got confiscated by
OL,10,Fthe patrolling police officers. We
OL,11,Fwere by no means the outliers. It was
OL,12,Fnormal for drunk teenagers to fill the
OL,13,Fparks and seafront on the blustery
OL,14,FKent coast at the weekend.
