OL,7,Falcohol provided more than any of my
OL,8,Ffriends. I thought alcohol, and in
OL,9,Fparticular vodka, was amazing. The
OL,10,Fconfidence it gave me, the way it
OL,11,Fchanged my mood ` it was addictive
OL,12,Ffrom day one.
