OL,6,FBy the age of 19, I was an alcoholic.
OL,7,FMy life soon spiralled into a seven-
OL,8,Fyear battle that caused unimaginable
OL,9,Fhurt to my family. Seven years of me
OL,10,Ftrying to shout louder than the
OL,11,Faddictive voice in my head telling me
OL,12,Fthat I "could drink like a normal
OL,13,Fperson". The truth was, I couldn't,
OL,14,Fand I will never be able to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/33
