OL,6,FI spent six months in rehab, lost
OL,7,Fseveral jobs, destroyed relationships
OL,8,Fand eventually ended up with alcoholic
OL,9,Fliver disease all before my 26th
OL,10,Fbirthday.
OL,12,FMy skin was jaundiced, and the whites
OL,13,Fof my eyes had turned a murky shade of
OL,14,Fyellow. The alcohol damaged the nerves
OL,15,Fin my legs and feet making them
OL,16,Fincredibly sensitive. My liver was
OL,17,Fhuge, fatty and scarred.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/33
