OL,6,FThankfully, we are living in a Britain
OL,7,Fwhere it has never been more socially
OL,8,Facceptable to be sober.
OL,10,FThe rise of low and no alcoholic
OL,11,Fdrinks, an increase in health-
OL,12,Fconsciousness, greater awareness of
OL,13,Fthe benefits of going alcohol free,
OL,14,Fand a noticeable reduction in sober-
OL,15,Fstigma has led to almost a fifth of
OL,16,Fthe population living a drink free
OL,17,Flifestyle now.
