OL,6,FI've been travelling around the
OL,7,Fcountry for ITV's Tonight Programme to
OL,8,Ffind out why, and more importantly,
OL,9,Fhow people are putting down the pints.
OL,11,FFirst up was Liverpool to meet a group
OL,12,Fof students who have been leading the
OL,13,Fcharge. Surprisingly, the sober
OL,14,Fmovement is being led by young people.
OL,15,FThe NHS Health Survey for England 2022
OL,16,Ffound that 26% of those aged 16-24 had
OL,17,Fnot had any alcohol across the
OL,18,Fprevious 12 months.
