OL,6,FThe Sober Soc is a 150+ strong sober
OL,7,Fsociety at the University of
OL,8,FLiverpool. They meet for weekly
OL,9,Fsocials like bingo, karaoke and
OL,10,Fquizzes. The group is open to everyone
OL,11,F` they just ask people not to drink at
OL,12,Ftheir events.
OL,14,FSome members I spoke to referenced
OL,15,Fcost, physical health and mental
OL,16,Fhealth as some of the reasons why they
OL,17,Fdo not drink. Perhaps more worryingly,
OL,18,Fseveral members said it was due to
OL,19,Ffears over their safety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/33
