OL,6,FLots of people drink alcohol in
OL,7,Fmoderation, and don't have issues with
OL,8,Fit. And some people don't have an
OL,9,Faddiction to it, but it still causes
OL,10,Fhavoc in their lives. That was the
OL,11,Fcase for Stacey from Hertfordshire.
OL,13,FA mum-of-two with a demanding sales
OL,14,Fjob, Stacey McMurrough says she would
OL,15,Fbinge drink which would leave her with
OL,16,Fblackouts, anxiety and hangovers which
OL,17,Fwould last three or four days. Her
OL,18,Fdrinking then increased when the
OL,19,Fnation went into lockdown during the
OL,20,Fpandemic.
