OL,6,FBut in March last year, Stacey decided
OL,7,Fthat it was time to stop drinking all
OL,8,Ftogether and she hasn't looked back
OL,9,Fsince. In fact this Christmas was her
OL,10,Ffirst sober one, and she documented it
OL,11,Ffor the programme.
OL,13,FShe says of her drinking days: "I was
OL,14,Flike 60 or 70 percent of myself. I
OL,15,Fjust got kind of tired of it. I just
OL,16,Fknew I had to change.
