OL,6,F"For me to be a hundred percent at
OL,7,Fwork, at home as a mother and as a
OL,8,Fwife, I just knew that I couldn't be a
OL,9,Fhundred percent at everything whilst
OL,10,Fhaving alcohol in my life."
OL,12,FStacey says that in less than a year
OL,13,Fof sobriety her health has improved
OL,14,Fconsiderably along with her sleeping
OL,15,Fpattern and energy levels. She
OL,16,Fattributes a lot of her success to
OL,17,Fsober social media, books and podcasts.
