OL,6,F"The benefits of it have been so good
OL,7,Fthat I can't see myself drinking
OL,8,Fagain. I've read books, listened to
OL,9,Fpodcasts and I (now) know the effects
OL,10,Fthat alcohol has on you, physically
OL,11,Fand mentally. And I just think, why
OL,12,Fwould I go back to that?"
OL,14,FThose sober books and podcasts
OL,15,Finspired Stacey to start recording her
OL,16,Fown journey on Instagram to try and
OL,17,Fhelp others. This is the pattern that
OL,18,Fis driving the sober movement.
