OL,6,FWe also spoke to Ricci and Alisha from
OL,7,FLondon who quit drinking after
OL,8,Frealising their relationship with
OL,9,Falcohol was no longer healthy.
OL,11,FAlisha started listening to podcasts
OL,12,Fto help her on her sober journey but
OL,13,Fsaid she found a gap in what was
OL,14,Favailable:
OL,16,F"I was struggling to find any people
OL,17,Ffrom the black community sharing their
OL,18,Fsober stories, particularly in the UK.
OL,19,FSo, I said, why don't we start up our
OL,20,Fown podcast and put ourselves out
OL,21,Fthere?"
