OL,3,CSobriety and alcohol deaths on the
OL,4,Crise - can the UK ditch booze?
OL,6,FAnd that's exactly what the couple
OL,7,Fdid. They started the Black and Sober
OL,8,FPodcast.
OL,10,F"I wanted to be more visible and show
OL,11,Fthat everybody has issues with it and
OL,12,Fit's not just a particular race,"
OL,13,FAlisha said.
OL,15,F"Our podcast isn't just for black
OL,16,Fpeople, it's for the whole sober
OL,17,Fcommunity or anyone that has been
OL,18,Fsober or trying to get sober or are
OL,19,Fsober curious," Ricci added.
