OL,3,CSobriety and alcohol deaths on the
OL,4,Crise - can the UK ditch booze?
OL,6,FDescribing his own experience, Ricci
OL,7,Fsaid: "Before I knew it, I was weeks,
OL,8,Fmonths into sobriety. And that was
OL,9,Fthrough me just taking one day at a
OL,10,Ftime".
OL,12,FThe rise in no and low alcoholic
OL,13,Fdrinks has also been helping some
OL,14,Fpeople curb their drinking and could
OL,15,Falso play its part in reducing alcohol
OL,16,Fharm. The IWSR (International Wines
OL,17,Fand Spirits Record) forecast the
OL,18,Findustry to grow at 7% over the next
OL,19,Ffive years. But question marks remain
OL,20,Fover how accessible the products are
OL,21,Fto everyone.
