OL,3,CSobriety and alcohol deaths on the
OL,4,Crise - can the UK ditch booze?
OL,6,F"And if this rise in sobriety is being
OL,7,Fdriven through social media or other
OL,8,Favenues, do they have access to that?
OL,9,FAre they seeing it?"
OL,11,F"Unless all parts of our population
OL,12,Fbuy into that cultural change, I don't
OL,13,Fthink we're going to see a dramatic
OL,14,Freduction in alcohol related deaths
OL,15,Fand specifically alcohol related liver
OL,16,Fdeaths."
OL,18,FThe good news for those who may have
OL,19,Fdamaged their health through drinking
OL,20,Fis that there is a way back.
