OL,3,CSobriety and alcohol deaths on the
OL,4,Crise - can the UK ditch booze?
OL,6,FOver the last 18 months I've undergone
OL,7,Fa full MOT on my liver. The results
OL,8,Fhave been truly remarkable.
OL,10,FBilirubin is one of the measurements
OL,11,Fused to assess liver health. It's a
OL,12,Fyellow substance that forms as a by-
OL,13,Fproduct when old red cells are broken
OL,14,Fdown. Too much of it turns you
OL,15,Fjaundice. A healthy range is anywhere
OL,16,Fbetween 0 ` 21.
