OL,3,CSobriety and alcohol deaths on the
OL,4,Crise - can the UK ditch booze?
OL,6,FWhen I was admitted to Kings in 2015
OL,7,Fmy bilirubin was 403. It's now 8. An
OL,8,Fultrasound revealed my liver is no
OL,9,Flonger fatty or enlarged. And, perhaps
OL,10,Fmost incredible of all, a fibroscan
OL,11,Fshowed my liver is no longer scarred.
OL,13,FMy liver, which was on brink of
OL,14,Fcirrhosis a decade ago, has completely
OL,15,Frecovered. I can't quite believe how
OL,16,Ffortunate I am to have made such a
OL,17,Fgreat recovery. I know for many people
OL,18,Fin a similar position the outcome can
OL,19,Fbe far worse.
