OL,3,CSobriety and alcohol deaths on the
OL,4,Crise - can the UK ditch booze?
OL,6,FI don't want anyone to go through the
OL,7,Fhell that alcohol put me and my family
OL,8,Fthrough. So, knowing that there is a
OL,9,Fgrowing sober movement and that
OL,10,Fattitudes towards alcohol are
OL,11,Fchanging, fills me with optimism.
OL,13,FHowever, it's not impacting public
OL,14,Fhealth yet - people are still dying in
OL,15,Frecord numbers from alcohol specific
OL,16,Fcauses.
